name: MFNY - Concentrate - Live Resin Badder - The Belefonte - 1g
description: Jump in the line! Belafontes premium structure and versatility make it a standout addition to the MFNY lineup. This cultivar comes to us via a collaboration between Masonic Seeds and Dammit Bobby, crossing Grape Tallyman with Honey Banana. Its development reflects a dedication to breeding precision and innovation. Belafonte features a dynamic flavor interplay, switching seamlessly between grape and banana notes on the inhale and exhale. This unique balance creates a playfully complex sensory experience that keeps people coming back for more. Its effects are balanced, offering a euphoric and relaxing high that resonates with recreational or medicinal benefits. Belafonte stands out for its structurally beautiful and robust plant form. Its dense buds display rich hues of purple and green, creating a striking visual appeal. This plant performs exceptionally both in cultivation and extraction, making for impressive weight and resin production. While its oil proved a bit too chunky for batter form, its debut in a 510 cart has quickly become a staff favorite, earning praise for its smooth, flavorful profile and unparalleled quality.

name: NY Honey - AIO - Grape Soda - 1g - Enhanced Resin
description:
Traditional Classification: Indica-Dominant Hybrid
Effects: Relaxing, Happy, Calm
Grape Soda is an indica-dominant hybrid combining classic grape-like aromas with calming, relaxing effects. Known as a phenotype of Tahoe OG Kush, New Yorkers appreciate this strain for its mellow physical relaxation paired with a carefree and tranquil state of mind. This 1G Enhanced Resin All-In-One Disposable Vape is made from butane hash oil extracted from fresh frozen flower. During extraction, certain delicate terpenes naturally diminish, so we enhance our resin by thoughtfully adding back authentic, strain-specific terpenes captured from our own freeze-dried hash. This meticulous reintroduction preserves the strains full flavor profile and ensures a clean, potent vaping experience without artificial additives.
Our 1-gram disposable vape features a next-generation ZeroScorch Ceramic Heating Core designed to preserve authentic terpenes and flavor profiles, delivering smooth vapor without scorching. Dual activation allows you to simply inhale or press the button for precise dosing. We recommend short 3-second inhales for the optimal experience.

name: NY Honey - AIO - Peach Ringz - 1g - Enhanced Resin
description:
Traditional Classification: Staiva-Dominant Hybrid
Effects: Creative, Euphoric, Relaxing
Peach Ringz is a Staiva-Dominant Hybrid strain known for gently relaxing effects and a cheerful, creative buzz. A cross between Marionberry and Eddy OG, Peach Ringz provides a balanced experience that inspires creativity and social interaction without heavy sedation. This 1G Enhanced Resin All-In-One Disposable Vape features butane hash oil extracted from fresh frozen flower. Because some delicate terpene profiles can diminish during extraction, we enhance our resin by carefully reintroducing cannabis-derived terpenes captured from our own in-house freeze-dried hash. This meticulous enhancement restores authentic aromas, preserves the strains full character, and ensures a pure, flavorful vaping experience without artificial additives.
Our 1-gram disposable vape features a next-generation ZeroScorch Ceramic Heating Core designed to preserve authentic terpenes and flavor profiles, delivering smooth vapor without scorching. Dual activation allows you to simply inhale or press the button for precise dosing. We recommend short 3-second inhales for the optimal experience.

name: Select ACE Terpologist - Brazzy Kush - 2g

brand.name: Grassroots
brand.description:
They say it all comes back to your roots, right?

Our roots, homegrown in a small house on the north side of Chicago. It was in that house we explored our connection to nature with inspiration from the city. It was in that house we brought creativity to cultivation. It was in that house we explored with craft strains and innovative genetics, and in that house, we knew we had to share our passion for premium cannabis with our friends, family and community.

Youll see our craft spirit reflected in everything we create and do. From our top-shelf flower to our all-ground, whole flower pre-rolls and variety of tasty concentrates, were here to celebrate cannabis and community in their most honest forms that nature and authenticity inspire.

Because while we may grow, our roots keep us grounded.

Grassroots. Its in our nature.

name: 1937 - Small Bud - Biker Kush - 7g
description:
Biker Kush is an Indica-dominant hybrid created by crossing the classic Hells Angels OG (HA-OG) x (HA-OG X SFV OG Kush BX2) strains. Perfect for any OG lover, Biker Kush packs a calming and lifted high that's super sociable and outgoing in nature from start to finish. Biker Kush is often chosen to treat those suffering from conditions such as inflammation, cramps, insomnia, depression, and chronic stress. This bud has a spicy fruity flavor with a sour citrus exhale accompanied by sweet woods and pines. The aroma is very earthy and citrusy with a sour spicy overtone that intensifies as the nugs are broken apart and burned away.
THC: 33.7%

Effects:
Calm. Happy, relaxed

name: Bouket - Flower - Blue Nerdz - 4g
description:
Blue Nerdz is a perfectly balanced hybrid strain that results from the combination of Forbidden Fruit and Watermelon Z. The characteristics of these parent strains contribute to the well-rounded effects, striking appearance, and memorable flavor of Blue Nerds. When these sparkling nugs are broken apart, they emit a delightful mix of fragrances, including sour citrus lemon, Granny Smith apples, and sweet blueberries. In terms of flavor, Blue Nerds offers a delightful experience for the palate. Each inhale presents a burst of sweet berries, crisp apples, and juicy melon, followed by a sugary aftertaste that remains on the tongue.
Dried cannabis flower is primarily ingested via inhalation. Activation time is roughly about 5 minutes and can last up to a few hours.
THC: 23.1%
Effects:
Calm, Happy, Relaxed

name: Grassroots - Delphi Diesel  - 3.5g
description:
Skunky, citrusy, and smooth, this old-school diesel fuel meets sharp notes for a punchy, fast-hitting ride you wont forget. Take yourself back to the golden days of Sour Diesel, this sativa fires up with a thick, nostril-tingling blast of straight gas. Its raw, skunky, and carries that unmistakable Chem-D punch, but with a smoothness that cuts the kick. The inhale delivers a sharp citrus bite, like lemon zest over pungent notes. The exhale settles into a deep, earthy fuel that clings to the senses with a tingly sweetness. This sativa is a full-throttle experience perfect for those who crave bold flavor and serious lift.
THC: 24.31%

brand.name: Grassroots
brand.description:
They say it all comes back to your roots, right?

Our roots, homegrown in a small house on the north side of Chicago. It was in that house we explored our connection to nature with inspiration from the city. It was in that house we brought creativity to cultivation. It was in that house we explored with craft strains and innovative genetics, and in that house, we knew we had to share our passion for premium cannabis with our friends, family and community.

Youll see our craft spirit reflected in everything we create and do. From our top-shelf flower to our all-ground, whole flower pre-rolls and variety of tasty concentrates, were here to celebrate cannabis and community in their most honest forms that nature and authenticity inspire.

Because while we may grow, our roots keep us grounded.

Grassroots. Its in our nature.

name: Grassroots - Foreign Kush Mints  - 3.5g
description:
Bigger, bolder, and built for the night, this extra-chunky Kush Mints brings sweet, doughy richness with a cosmic-level kick so you can fade into the stars. Like a mint on your pillow, this heavy-hitting indica puts you down in delicious fashion. Foreign Kush Mints has an aroma that hits like a wave of pine and menthol, with a sweet, doughy richness underneath. The inhale is fresh and cool before settling into a creamy, nutty and earthy warmth. This heavy-hitting indica tastes as good as it feels with a quick onset and starry-eyed experience. Settle in and let the smoke take over, this sofa-tested strain tests up to 32% THC levels.
THC: 31.12%

name: Livwell - WOmac - 14g
description:
Watermelon MAC is a hybrid cross of Watermelon Zkittlez and MAC (Miracle Alien Cookies) both strains known for their flavor and potency. The Watermelon Zkittlez brings a fruity sweetness and subtle gassy backend, while MAC contributes to structure, trichome coverage, and a classic hybrid high with cookie-forward funk.
WoMAC is Indica that leans slightly toward the energetic and uplifting side of things not racy like a full sativa, but also not couch-lock territory. With over 3.49% total terpenes, . The presence of terpinolene, limonene, and beta-myrcene gives the flower a citrus-forward, piney, slightly floral edge with lingering hints of gassy sweetness when ground.
THC: 25.67%

name: Small A$$ Buds - Small Bud - Zourz - 14g
description:
Zours, also known simply as Zour, is an indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through crossing the iconic Gelato X Zkittlez strains. With a name like this, you know that you're in for one super sour flavor with this bud. Zours packs a lip-puckering sour citrus flavor with a potent punch of buttery nuttiness and sweet fruits. The aroma is just as heavy, with a super sour overtone accented by lemony citrus, fresh fruits and earthy nuttiness. The Zours high will hit you almost as soon as you exhale, filling your mind with a lifted sense of happiness that's not too vibrant. Rather, your mind will feel tingly and stimulated, not really able to focus on much of anything at all. At the same time, a physical tingle will begin to creep into your body, eventually turning into a fully-fledged buzz that has you fully relaxed, hopelessly couch-locked and pretty sleepy. Combined with its high 14-18% average THC level and 0-1% average CBD level, these long-lasting effects make Zours a great choice for treating a variety of conditions including chronic stress or anxiety, insomnia, chronic pain and cramps or muscle spasms. This bud has dense flat tree-shaped forest green nugs with dark leaves, thin orange hairs and frosty, amber-tinted white crystal trichomes
THC: 19.2%

name: Space Buds - Infused Flower - Moonrocks Blueberry Muffin - 4g
description:
Traditional Classification: Indica
Effects: Relaxation, Euphoria, Uplifting, Calming
Embark on a delicious journey with SPACEBUDS Moonrocks - Blueberry Muffin! These moonrocks are drenched in rich Hash Rosin and infused with a proprietary terpene blend. Each nugget is then coated in kief, delivering a potent and flavorful experience reminiscent of freshly baked blueberry muffins. Enjoy the calming, euphoric, and uplifting effects that will transport you to a state of blissful relaxation. Discover the exceptional quality and innovation of Veterans Choice Creations in every puff.
THC: 62.5%

Handling and Preparation: Avoid grinding Moon Rocks as you would with regular cannabis flowers. Instead, cut small pieces from the rock to prevent loss of concentrate and kief. Use tools like scissors, a sharp knife, or a razor for precision.
Handling and Preparation: Avoid grinding Moon Rocks as you would with regular cannabis flowers. Instead, cut small pieces from the rock to prevent loss of concentrate and kief. Use tools like scissors, a sharp knife, or a razor for precision.

Consumption Method: It's recommended to smoke Moon Rocks using glassware, such as a pipe or bong. This ensures that the oil and kief components burn correctly. Packing the bowl loosely allows for better airflow, minimizing the chances of clogging.

Mix with Flower for Easier Lighting: Moon Rocks can be difficult to light due to their dense and oil-rich composition. Placing small pieces on top of ground cannabis flower in your smoking device can help maintain the flame and enjoy the intense effects.

name: B Noble - Pre Roll 2pk - Mimosa Kush Mints - 2g
description:
(2) 1g Pre Rolls
This delicious bud offers a super balanced high with giddy, giggly effects and an amazing taste to go right along with it. The Mimosa Kush Mints high will settle in slowly, creeping in with warming waves of relaxing calm that gently inch their way throughout mind and body. You'll feel hazy yet happy with a sense of giddy bliss that will leave you giggling uncontrollably for no reason at all. Your body will begin to settle down next, sinking into the couch with a weighty and soothing sense that has you ready to kick back and enjoy your afternoon.
ABOUT B NOBLE
The high-quality cannabis products B NOBLE sells in nine states helps Bernard Noble and his family. We also donate a portion of our sales revenue to organizations committed to helping those who have been impacted by the U.S. criminal justice systems harsh sentences for nonviolent cannabis offenders. Bernard Noble represents the countless nonviolent cannabis victims serving time to this very day. Alongside our U.S. partner, Curaleaf, we have worked side by side towards our mission to raise awareness around these unjust drug laws. When you choose B NOBLE you choose to be a part of the work righting the deeply embedded wrongs of the past and pave a path to the future where nonviolent cannabis criminality falls into the trash can of history.

name: Dank - Pre Roll - Afghani - 1g
description: A pre-roll joint of premium DANK AFGHANI flower rolled in classic joint paper. Afghani is a legendary indica strain known for its roots in the ancient landscapes of Afghanistan, the origin of many classic cannabis varieties. Renowned for its heavy resin production inherited genetically through generations, Afghani offers a deeply soothing experience, marked by a sweet and earthy flavor profile. It envelops users in a profound state of relaxation and euphoria, making it a favorite among those seeking relief from insomnia, pain, and stress. This strains potent effects also stimulate appetite, making it an ideal choice for medical marijuana patients needing to manage physical discomfort and enhance their overall wellbeing.

brand.name: Grassroots
brand.description:
They say it all comes back to your roots, right?

Our roots, homegrown in a small house on the north side of Chicago. It was in that house we explored our connection to nature with inspiration from the city. It was in that house we brought creativity to cultivation. It was in that house we explored with craft strains and innovative genetics, and in that house, we knew we had to share our passion for premium cannabis with our friends, family and community.

Youll see our craft spirit reflected in everything we create and do. From our top-shelf flower to our all-ground, whole flower pre-rolls and variety of tasty concentrates, were here to celebrate cannabis and community in their most honest forms that nature and authenticity inspire.

Because while we may grow, our roots keep us grounded.

Grassroots. Its in our nature.

name: MFNY - Infused Pre Roll - Electric Lime - 0.75g
description: Electric Lime is MFNY's first creation from its in-house breeding project. The result of a small tester batch, this is a standout phenotype that shines brighter than the visuals generated by its namesake. Electric Lime produces flavors and aromas that are equally striking as its appearance. With a nostalgic start that is reminiscent of the cherry Ak-47 leading the way, exhale makes for a distinct sharp lime citrus finish coming close behind, this is a flavor profile that offers up both sweet and tangy notes. Which takes the senses on a wild, enjoyable ride from first smell to final inhale. Shining brightly with its chunky, round colas and glistening platinum trichomes against neon green buds, Electric Lime is a real eye-catcher. A righteous representation of MFNYs breeding expertise, this is a cultivar that stands out visually and experientially. Electricity and citrusy, whats not to like?

name: Pot & Head - Infused Blunt - Jack & Grape - 3.5g
description:
This blunts got that wake-you-up and lay-you-down kinda vibe. Jack and Grape hits your head with a bright, focused buzz while your body melts into a smooth grape haze. Rolled up with 3 grams of Jack and Grape flower and half a gram of bubble hash, then wrapped in Terp Infused Juicy Hemp Wraps for that slow, sticky burn. Glass tip on deck to keep every pull cool and clean.
Light this up when you wanna feel good but still keep your eyes open. Perfect for rolling through your day with a smile or spacing out with the homies talking about absolutely nothing. Jack and Grape because sometimes you need to feel lifted and laid back at the same time.
